> 输出："a aef qerf bb"
> ```
>
> 
>
> **限制：**
>
> ```
> 0 <= path.length <= 10000
> ```
>
> Related Topics
>
> 字符串

```java
class Solution {
    public String pathEncryption(String path) {
        return path.replace('.',' ');
    }
}
```

还是用双指针(单指针)做一下：

```java
class Solution {
    public String pathEncryption(String path) {
        char[]chars=path.toCharArray();
        for (int i = 0; i < path.length(); i++) {
            if(chars[i]=='.'){
                chars[i]=' ';
            }
        }
        return String.copyValueOf(chars);
    }
}
